{"tid":2157484,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"胡鴻鈞居澳洲胞姊驚艷 網民：靚過今屆港姐","createTime":"2020-08-15T05:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T16:19:31.000Z","uid":44730,"like":42,"dislike":486,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"84771c5024348b0c1d11747fca850dd8cd9c2504","tid":2157484,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"現年30歲的胡鴻鈞，加入無綫八年，雖然間中都會提及媽咪及胞姊，不過，直至近日為媽慶生，才令網民驚為天人，原來他一直有個索家姐Sharon，胞姊更被網民大起底，摷出她唔少靚相，定居澳洲的Sharon眼大大輪廓精緻，更被指靚過今屆港姐，提議Hubert叫靚家姐入行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/img_9159_10354582435f365d807a4e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fimg_9159_10354582435f365d807a4e4.jpg&h=ed127902&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d844d7ee1e339f367a741258922a3eae6a85e409","tid":2157484,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"近日在IG上載為母親慶生的合照，更留言笑阿媽：「我娘親最近嘅口頭禪係 : 『食埋呢一餐減肥』hmm&hellip;似乎呢一餐食左幾十年都未食完，媽，生日快樂！祝您身體健康、繼續有氣有力，但可以少啲囉唆。」更大爆阿媽貪靚，影了多張相才滿意效果。"},{"pid":"1a433379e73b252bfb037ea77ad7f3a0bba9109b","tid":2157484,"uid":44730,"like":13,"dislike":125,"score":-112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/img_9160_16018619585f365d838955f-1024x1017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fimg_9160_16018619585f365d838955f-1024x1017.jpg&h=fe5df51a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b947071790c4bcdb8cd20ca71f40962456e9433","tid":2157484,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"不過，最矚目唔係佢媽咪，而係Hubert遠在澳洲的胞姊Sharon轉貼細佬與媽媽的合照，令網民突然留意她。Sharon原來是一名大眼美女，輪廓鮮明，還擁有甜美笑容。"},{"pid":"8af7cbf2590217d94472adc5f0e7312dceef7d5f","tid":2157484,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":141,"score":-139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/img_9162_12446833315f365d88d6aba-1024x914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fimg_9162_12446833315f365d88d6aba-1024x914.jpg&h=cb46fd52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27b1c27c69094b0a8947defefff4c55deb609142","tid":2157484,"uid":217336,"like":110,"dislike":9,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"哨牙㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7276dbf664e54b5ed043240b9a87bacc85f897","tid":2157484,"uid":274094,"like":243,"dislike":2,"score":241,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"邊個叫網民"},{"pid":"e966b7d4f1c57184fc8b508a584b2da4df86a2a4","tid":2157484,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":141,"score":-135,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/img_9174_3681037285f365d688c3b8-982x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fimg_9174_3681037285f365d688c3b8-982x1024.jpg&h=691526ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姐姐Sharon是一位大美女，粉絲更問：「做咩唔入行？」"},{"pid":"a5310412ec6193de68ccd7cf3cb08d511a8911d6","tid":2157484,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":134,"score":-132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/img_9173_10624046465f365d6537a61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fimg_9173_10624046465f365d6537a61.jpg&h=ff6884b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f9529d881a07d4cfd41be2bc3f95860f00bd4dd","tid":2157484,"uid":44730,"like":14,"dislike":94,"score":-80,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/img_9168_79015